{"lang":"ja","stage":6,"title":"longer everyday sentences","sentences":[{"t":"パーティー行ったよ。","en":"I went to the party.","r":"Pātī itta yo.","a":"n_cac1f6073b2f.mp3"},{"t":"パーティー来る？","en":"Are you coming to the party?","r":"Pātī kuru?","a":"n_975e109547d4.mp3"},{"t":"バスもう来てるよ。","en":"The bus is coming now.","r":"Basu mō kiteru yo.","a":"n_2d65ed017b9f.mp3"},{"t":"この近くに住んでるよ。","en":"I live close to here.","r":"Kono chikaku ni sunderu yo.","a":"n_6a3381680ef3.mp3"},{"t":"彼みんな知ってるんだよ。","en":"He knows everyone.","r":"Kare minna shitteru n da yo.","a":"n_dcd45652e98f.mp3"},{"t":"頭が痛い。","en":"My head hurts.","r":"Atama ga itai.","a":"n_3bf1560bd080.mp3"},{"t":"五分で着くよ。","en":"It arrives in five minutes.","r":"Go-fun de tsuku yo.","a":"n_3af30da21736.mp3"},{"t":"本当のこと言ったほうがいいよ。","en":"You should tell the truth.","r":"Hontō no koto itta hō ga ii yo.","a":"n_955d2969ba6e.mp3"},{"t":"ちょっと休んだほうがいいよ。","en":"You should rest a little.","r":"Chotto yasunda hō ga ii yo.","a":"n_7a769f7adec2.mp3"},{"t":"これすごくおいしい。","en":"This is delicious.","r":"Kore sugoku oishii.","a":"n_32522d652538.mp3"},{"t":"もう待てない。","en":"I can't wait any longer.","r":"Mō matenai.","a":"n_d83436e480a1.mp3"},{"t":"どうなるか見たいんだ。","en":"I want to see what happens.","r":"Dō naru ka mitai n da.","a":"n_89127c548419.mp3"},{"t":"一時間で戻るよ。","en":"I'll be back in an hour.","r":"Ichi-jikan de modoru yo.","a":"n_fd6ab0be2044.mp3"},{"t":"なにか飲みたい。","en":"I want something to drink.","r":"Nanika nomitai.","a":"n_91f9ecd09599.mp3"},{"t":"なに飲む？","en":"What are you going to drink?","r":"Nani nomu?","a":"n_659e81f9ac03.mp3"},{"t":"水でいいや。","en":"I'll have water.","r":"Mizu de ii ya.","a":"n_1cdc91811ee5.mp3"},{"t":"今回は私が払うよ。","en":"This time I'm paying.","r":"Konkai wa watashi ga harau yo.","a":"n_6fabb4c6d5fb.mp3"},{"t":"右側だよ。","en":"It's on the right.","r":"Migigawa da yo.","a":"n_788efd4e9e0a.mp3"},{"t":"右に曲がって。","en":"Turn right.","r":"Migi ni magatte.","a":"n_82a67bf53a75.mp3"},{"t":"タクシーで行ったほうがいいよ。","en":"Better go by taxi.","r":"Takushī de itta hō ga ii yo.","a":"n_7ea05264d789.mp3"},{"t":"彼女は友達だよ。","en":"She's my friend.","r":"Kanojo wa tomodachi da yo.","a":"n_1757a1cfa83f.mp3"},{"t":"彼女、君の友達？","en":"Is she your friend?","r":"Kanojo, kimi no tomodachi?","a":"n_730456d92090.mp3"},{"t":"こちら友達だよ。","en":"This is my friend.","r":"Kochira tomodachi da yo.","a":"n_8961d02f83c9.mp3"},{"t":"やっと金曜だ。","en":"It's finally Friday.","r":"Yatto kin'yō da.","a":"n_074f7e21f3e5.mp3"},{"t":"会えてうれしいよ。","en":"I'm happy to see you.","r":"Aete ureshii yo.","a":"n_684c9dd44388.mp3"},{"t":"あとで会いに行くね。","en":"I'm coming to see you later.","r":"Ato de ai ni iku ne.","a":"n_d24f0afef54b.mp3"},{"t":"彼女猫飼ってるんだ。","en":"She has a cat.","r":"Kanojo neko katteru n da.","a":"n_edb19f911b16.mp3"},{"t":"家にいたいな。","en":"I'd rather stay home.","r":"Ie ni itai na.","a":"n_8bad3a7420fb.mp3"},{"t":"遅れちゃうよ。","en":"We're going to be late.","r":"Okurechau yo.","a":"n_df7297ec33aa.mp3"},{"t":"お願いしてもいい？","en":"Can you do me a favor?","r":"Onegai shite mo ii?","a":"n_6c86629e8bc6.mp3"},{"t":"ここなにがおいしいの？","en":"What's good here?","r":"Koko nani ga oishii no?","a":"n_5681a80d4194.mp3"},{"t":"いいほうに考えなよ。","en":"Look on the bright side.","r":"Ii hō ni kangae na yo.","a":"n_501cb1811d15.mp3"},{"t":"ちゃんとした理由を一つ言って。","en":"Give me one good reason.","r":"Chanto shita riyū o hitotsu itte.","a":"n_c17c2abff811.mp3"},{"t":"こっちのほうが簡単だよ。","en":"This is easier.","r":"Kotchi no hō ga kantan da yo.","a":"n_c6fc3bce2680.mp3"},{"t":"前はもっと簡単だったのに。","en":"It used to be easier.","r":"Mae wa motto kantan datta no ni.","a":"n_5245c06f3fc4.mp3"},{"t":"左側だよ。","en":"It's on the left.","r":"Hidarigawa da yo.","a":"n_e7f8ae3cface.mp3"},{"t":"左に曲がって。","en":"Turn left.","r":"Hidari ni magatte.","a":"n_2dc906ef75b9.mp3"},{"t":"駅に行くよ。","en":"I'm going to the station.","r":"Eki ni iku yo.","a":"n_60e6661181f5.mp3"},{"t":"駅どこ？","en":"Where is the station?","r":"Eki doko?","a":"n_128faac74345.mp3"},{"t":"昨日おいしいもの食べたよ。","en":"I ate something tasty yesterday.","r":"Kinō oishii mono tabeta yo.","a":"n_fdb62181784b.mp3"},{"t":"始める準備できてるよ。","en":"I'm ready to start.","r":"Hajimeru junbi dekiteru yo.","a":"n_d9a6aecb42ca.mp3"},{"t":"ちょっとは料理できるよ。","en":"I know how to cook a little.","r":"Chotto wa ryōri dekiru yo.","a":"n_0e8f3530c09c.mp3"},{"t":"そんなのだれも買わないよ。","en":"Nobody wants to buy that.","r":"Sonna no dare mo kawanai yo.","a":"n_2e0627ab3476.mp3"},{"t":"五ユーロ貸してるよ。","en":"You owe me five euros.","r":"Go yūro kashiteru yo.","a":"n_4fc5adda16e3.mp3"},{"t":"道よく知ってるよ。","en":"I know the way well.","r":"Michi yoku shitteru yo.","a":"n_a37742e08c90.mp3"},{"t":"今夜は出かけないよ。","en":"I'm not going out tonight.","r":"Kon'ya wa dekakenai yo.","a":"n_add85a02c763.mp3"},{"t":"一つ聞いていい？","en":"Can I ask one thing?","r":"Hitotsu kiite ii?","a":"n_4ccac6cf8f3c.mp3"},{"t":"これどう言えばいいかな。","en":"How do I tell you this?","r":"Kore dō ieba ii ka na.","a":"n_8f01fed5f81a.mp3"},{"t":"彼になんて言おう？","en":"What do I tell him now?","r":"Kare ni nan te iō?","a":"n_8ce80c914d77.mp3"},{"t":"彼は答え知ってるよ。","en":"He knows the answer.","r":"Kare wa kotae shitteru yo.","a":"n_67b2391986ba.mp3"},{"t":"彼女にお礼言ったよ。","en":"I thanked her.","r":"Kanojo ni orei itta yo.","a":"n_dcf72f9f1601.mp3"},{"t":"まだ準備できてないんだ。","en":"We're not ready yet.","r":"Mada junbi dekitenai n da.","a":"n_78a52816f0fd.mp3"},{"t":"考える時間がいるんだ。","en":"I need time to think.","r":"Kangaeru jikan ga iru n da.","a":"n_0a11ea25dab0.mp3"},{"t":"うち狭いんだ。","en":"My house is small.","r":"Uchi semai n da.","a":"n_b8f9171aeeff.mp3"},{"t":"うち狭いんだ。","en":"We have a small house.","r":"Uchi semai n da.","a":"n_b8f9171aeeff.mp3"},{"t":"この曲好き。","en":"I like this song.","r":"Kono kyoku suki.","a":"n_ff54ac6bba9c.mp3"},{"t":"なにも言ってないよ。","en":"I didn't say anything.","r":"Nani mo ittenai yo.","a":"n_05e4de59ec19.mp3"},{"t":"もう使い方わかってるよ。","en":"I already know how it works.","r":"Mō tsukaikata wakatteru yo.","a":"n_7bc6e4cb9697.mp3"},{"t":"彼女早起きなんだ。","en":"She gets up early.","r":"Kanojo hayaoki na n da.","a":"n_4e45b928f65a.mp3"},{"t":"飲み物なにがある？","en":"What do you have to drink?","r":"Nomimono nani ga aru?","a":"n_89751995dfd8.mp3"},{"t":"パンもう少しもらえる？","en":"Can you bring me more bread?","r":"Pan mō sukoshi moraeru?","a":"n_d068ba25663f.mp3"},{"t":"彼女は実家暮らしだよ。","en":"She lives at home.","r":"Kanojo wa jikkagurashi da yo.","a":"n_e290b86e7f92.mp3"},{"t":"六時まで仕事だよ。","en":"I work until six.","r":"Roku-ji made shigoto da yo.","a":"n_e49eda64bbf2.mp3"},{"t":"スマホ売りたいんだ。","en":"I want to sell my phone.","r":"Sumaho uritai n da.","a":"n_c263eb2bc6c5.mp3"},{"t":"チケットどこで買うの？","en":"Where do I buy the ticket?","r":"Chiketto doko de kau no?","a":"n_1bd52b6c0af3.mp3"},{"t":"喉が痛い。","en":"My throat hurts.","r":"Nodo ga itai.","a":"n_e0584019f9bb.mp3"},{"t":"彼は友達だよ。","en":"He's a friend of mine.","r":"Kare wa tomodachi da yo.","a":"n_9fc479151ff8.mp3"},{"t":"こちらこそ。","en":"The pleasure is mine.","r":"Kochira koso.","a":"n_5ca332aca2f4.mp3"},{"t":"今日はすごく忙しいんだ。","en":"I'm really busy today.","r":"Kyō wa sugoku isogashii n da.","a":"n_5b3db745dc26.mp3"},{"t":"友達みんなうれしそうだよ。","en":"My friends are happy.","r":"Tomodachi minna ureshisō da yo.","a":"n_bbf206216b2a.mp3"},{"t":"帰るの寂しいな。","en":"I'm sad to leave.","r":"Kaeru no sabishii na.","a":"n_2b1d7da5a8ae.mp3"},{"t":"早く着くことほとんどないんだ。","en":"I almost never arrive early.","r":"Hayaku tsuku koto hotondo nai n da.","a":"n_c4ae2d2eece9.mp3"},{"t":"今なにか食べなきゃ。","en":"We need to eat something now.","r":"Ima nanika tabenakya.","a":"n_e7a057cd9b21.mp3"},{"t":"チョコ大好き。","en":"I love chocolate.","r":"Choko daisuki.","a":"n_ac1fe2801c93.mp3"},{"t":"お日さま好き。","en":"I like the sun.","r":"Ohisama suki.","a":"n_517faf0a7d7c.mp3"},{"t":"コーヒーと紅茶どっちがいい？","en":"Do you prefer coffee or tea?","r":"Kōhī to kōcha dotchi ga ii?","a":"n_9defc3c0b27d.mp3"},{"t":"近いうちに会いたいな。","en":"I'd like to see you soon.","r":"Chikai uchi ni aitai na.","a":"n_f613efa1f15b.mp3"},{"t":"今は言えないんだ。","en":"I can't tell you now.","r":"Ima wa ienai n da.","a":"n_e30b1996f538.mp3"},{"t":"今日はすごく早く着いたよ。","en":"I got here really early today.","r":"Kyō wa sugoku hayaku tsuita yo.","a":"n_0c9e435439a6.mp3"},{"t":"彼女も一緒に来るよ。","en":"She's coming with us.","r":"Kanojo mo issho ni kuru yo.","a":"n_4dfd7c0669a0.mp3"},{"t":"あと五分で出るよ。","en":"We're leaving in five minutes.","r":"Ato go-fun de deru yo.","a":"n_3e132df1d86f.mp3"},{"t":"宿題もうやった？","en":"Did you do the homework yet?","r":"Shukudai mō yatta?","a":"n_6da01614763e.mp3"},{"t":"なんでそんなに聞くの？","en":"Why do you ask so much?","r":"Nande sonna ni kiku no?","a":"n_7891fc4fb4f1.mp3"},{"t":"彼って質問多いんだよね。","en":"He asks a lot of questions.","r":"Kare tte shitsumon ōi n da yo ne.","a":"n_5fc5e9be5405.mp3"},{"t":"だれにもなにも言いたくない。","en":"I don't want to tell anyone anything.","r":"Dare ni mo nani mo iitakunai.","a":"n_63c8e2b77b72.mp3"},{"t":"じゃあ昼にね。","en":"See you this afternoon.","r":"Jā hiru ni ne.","a":"n_33b60011f010.mp3"},{"t":"彼の名前知らないんだ。","en":"I don't know his name.","r":"Kare no namae shiranai n da.","a":"n_2c6a81240f8b.mp3"},{"t":"彼女は私のこと知ってるんだ。","en":"She knows my story.","r":"Kanojo wa watashi no koto shitteru n da.","a":"n_13919531f1cd.mp3"},{"t":"手が痛い。","en":"My hand hurts.","r":"Te ga itai.","a":"n_b79976ca5b79.mp3"},{"t":"番号教えるね。","en":"I'll give you my number.","r":"Bangō oshieru ne.","a":"n_a3d953f8712f.mp3"},{"t":"やり方見せて。","en":"Show me how it's done.","r":"Yarikata misete.","a":"n_56494d7e1be0.mp3"},{"t":"約束したよね。","en":"I gave you my word.","r":"Yakusoku shita yo ne.","a":"n_c38ebfc17d17.mp3"},{"t":"ちょっとちょうだい？","en":"Will you give me some?","r":"Chotto chōdai?","a":"n_9b486fedd49a.mp3"},{"t":"彼の私への目つき見た？","en":"Did you see how he looked at me?","r":"Kare no watashi e no metsuki mita?","a":"n_f574a2402265.mp3"}]}